v2.0.0 - decorations, summer, and traveling salesman!

New Content:
+ 2 New Summer Crates, which includes 13 new items.
+ New Twitch Secret, available in all crates, whenever derpmonster83 is live on Twitch.
+ New Rebirth!
+ ..Alien Event has ended.. [X]
+ Traveling Salesman, which has Alien Items (if you missed them), and brand new decoration items!
+ New Enchanting mastery, Unbox Slot mastery, and Luck mastery upgrades.
+ Decorations! Decorate your base with up to 10 different decorations. More base decoration options to come soon!
+ Earn +2 Luck, and a derp-themed decoration, by liking the game and joining the Derp LLC group.
+ NEW CODE: 'auxinite'
+ Added background music to the game. [X]

Balance Changes:
+ Uranium Ore is no longer affected by Toxic/Nuclear effects. Will not die to them. [X]
+ Colossal Stone Dropper ore is now worth $1M at base. [X]
+ Enforced Upgrader no longer has an upgrade range. [X]
+ Sugarbomb lifespan has increased from 45-75 seconds to 60-75 seconds. [X]
+ Corium now recieves a 1.1x upgrade whenever it consumes another ore with an effect, with a cap of 8 consumptions. Any other consumption will stop upgrading the ore.
+ Increased speed of Azure Scanner from 6 studs/s -> 10 studs/s [X]

Bug Fixes:
+ Buffs are now visible when advanced stats are toggled.
+ Sandstone Ore now changes to glass whenever the fire effect is applied, not just by the Ore Flamethrower.
+ Fixed Parasitic Fiend description wording to be clearer. [X]
+ Fixed a few floating point issues with numbers in upgrade descriptions. [X]
+ Fixed the Scarabyte ore and icon [X]
+ Potion Timer and Event timer now update on the same interval, and update at the same speed. -- cache time, ends in unix, and then update whenever player rejoins. save leave time in data
+ Fixed incorrect spelling inside of invalid code warning. [X]
+ Changed the event algorithm, to ensure parity across all timezones and CPU clocks. (fixes displaying wrong event + events happening early)
+ Offline Earning now works.
+ Fixed gui overlapping with current event and admin abuse.
+ Unbox Slot potion now says increases unbox slots by +1 instead of 1%
+ Fixed a bug where enchanter didn't update immediately when on high ping.
+ Removed effects from Crimson Pillars ore (it was reported to lag some clients).
+ Removed electrified visual perisisting after an ore is washed. [X]
+ Added an additional check to prevent ore from being stuck forever (removed Teleporting flag, and checks if a cloned ore hasn't moved after so many ticks)
+ Events have moved back to being every 30 minutes, at the top of the hour, not offset by 15 minutes.
+ Removed 'None' notification when no event is happening.
+ Auto-buying a crate will continue, even if you cannot afford it after rejoining.
+ Enchanter no longer flashes an expensive price before adjusting to the correct price for skipping. 
+ If inventory errors/fails, it will automatically skip and complete, logging the change for fixing later. This fixes all people soft-locked in the inventory.

Changes:
+ NEW SETTING: Force nighttime/daytime. Crystal comets will still happen on the same interval.
+ NEW SETTING: Enable/disable leaderboard chat tags.
+ Inventory now force completes when you rejoin the game. 
+ Added a tooltip for the current potion you are upgrading to in the brewery.
+ If you are on a leaderboard, your name will be highlighted.
+ Plot was changed to accomodate more crates.
+ Droppers with neon ore now have a description indicating so.
+ Secrets show up in middle of screen when unboxxed.
+ Enabled resetting your avatar. [X]
+ 'derpmonster83' in global announcements is now colored orange.
+ Potions now pause when the luck is being overriden.
+ New base indicator that tells you whose base is whose, and a teleport back to your base button.
+ For new players, earn a free Legendary for turning on notifications.
+ Odds for items in crates now adjust based on your current luck.
+ Potion crafting now increments by '5', as opposed to one.
+ Revamped settings, see your global stats
+ Parasitic Fiend now retroactively fills index slots [X]
+ Added a countdown to the premium shop for Limited items.
+ Enchant Skipping now scales off of previous prices. See prices below.
common: 100 crystals
uncommon: 500 crystals
rare: 10K crystals
epic: 100k crystals
legendary: 500k crystals
secret: 2.5M crystals


